createView.selectQuery:
SELECT applications_0.id,
    applications_0.specimen_id,
    applications_0.product_id,
    product_1.name AS productname,
    applications_0.date,
    applications_0.amount,
    applications_0.method,
    applications_0.care_id
   FROM (blackseeds_applications applications_0
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_products product_1 ON (((applications_0.product_id)::text = (product_1.id)::text)));

SELECT id,
    description,
    type,
    step
   FROM blackseeds_attributes attributes_0;

SELECT ratings_0.id,
    strain_1.id AS strainid,
    ratings_0.value,
    strain_1.name AS strainname,
    attribute_2.id AS attributeid,
    attribute_2.description,
    attribute_2.type,
    attribute_2.step,
    ratings_0.strain_id,
    strain_1.tagid,
    ratings_0.attribute_id,
    ratings_0.createdby,
    ratings_0.createdat,
    ratings_0.modifiedat,
    ratings_0.comments,
    specimen_3.id AS specimenid,
    specimen_3.tagid AS specimentag,
    ratings_0.specimen_id
   FROM (((blackseeds_ratings ratings_0
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_strains strain_1 ON (((ratings_0.strain_id)::text = (strain_1.id)::text)))
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_attributes attribute_2 ON (((ratings_0.attribute_id)::text = (attribute_2.id)::text)))
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_specimens specimen_3 ON (((ratings_0.specimen_id)::text = (specimen_3.id)::text)));

SELECT cares_0.id,
    cares_0.specimen_id,
    caretype_1.name AS carename,
    caretype_1.description AS cared,
    caretype_1.caldaytype AS daytype,
    caretype_1.icon,
    cares_0.caretype_id,
    cares_0.date,
    cares_0.description
   FROM (blackseeds_cares cares_0
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_caretypes caretype_1 ON (((cares_0.caretype_id)::text = (caretype_1.id)::text)));

SELECT specimens_0.id,
    specimens_0.parentid,
    specimens_0.name,
    specimens_0.breedtype,
    specimens_0.seqnumber,
    specimens_0.tagid,
    specimens_0.planteddate,
    specimens_0.strain_id,
    specimens_0.sex,
    state_2.color AS statecolor,
    state_2.icon AS stateicon,
    state_2.description AS statedescription,
    specimens_0.state_id,
    strain_1.id AS strainid,
    strain_1.alias AS strainalias,
    strain_1.name AS strainname,
    max(cares_3.date) AS lastcare,
    0 AS photosnumber,
    specimens_0.favorite,
    COALESCE(avg(ratings_4.value), (0)::numeric) AS totalpoints
   FROM ((((blackseeds_specimens specimens_0
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_strains strain_1 ON (((specimens_0.strain_id)::text = (strain_1.id)::text)))
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_specimenstates state_2 ON (((specimens_0.state_id)::text = (state_2.id)::text)))
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_cares cares_3 ON (((cares_3.specimen_id)::text = (specimens_0.id)::text)))
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_ratings ratings_4 ON (((ratings_4.specimen_id)::text = (specimens_0.id)::text)))
  GROUP BY specimens_0.id, strain_1.name, strain_1.id, state_2.color, state_2.icon, state_2.description;

SELECT id,
    name,
    description
   FROM blackseeds_caretypes caretypes_0;

SELECT id,
    days,
    description,
    caldaytype,
    sequence
   FROM blackseeds_lifecycles lifecycles_0;

SELECT photos_0.id,
    photos_0.specimen_id,
    specimen_1.planteddate,
    photos_0.date,
    photos_0.publicid
   FROM (blackseeds_photos photos_0
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_specimens specimen_1 ON (((photos_0.specimen_id)::text = (specimen_1.id)::text)));

SELECT id,
    name,
    type,
    description,
    instructions,
    unit,
    false AS selected,
    0 AS amount
   FROM blackseeds_products products_0;

SELECT strains_0.id,
    strains_0.tagid,
    strains_0.name,
    strains_0.name AS strainname,
    strains_0.alias,
    COALESCE(avg(ratings_1.value), (0)::numeric) AS totalpoints
   FROM (blackseeds_strains strains_0
     LEFT JOIN blackseeds_ratings ratings_1 ON (((ratings_1.strain_id)::text = (strains_0.id)::text)))
  GROUP BY strains_0.id;

SELECT id,
    description,
    icon,
    color
   FROM blackseeds_specimenstates specimenstates_0;

SELECT id,
    specimen_id,
    specimen_id AS specimenid,
    date,
    liters,
    temp,
    ec,
    ph,
    method,
    care_id
   FROM blackseeds_waterings waterings_0;

SELECT st_0.id,
    st_0.description,
    st_0.color,
    st_0.icon,
    count(s_1.id) AS numberof
   FROM (blackseedsservice_specimenstates st_0
     LEFT JOIN blackseedsservice_specimens s_1 ON (((st_0.id)::text = (s_1.state_id)::text)))
  GROUP BY st_0.id, st_0.description, st_0.color, st_0.icon
 HAVING (count(s_1.id) > 0);
